name: Twittering Love
description:
Print your own wedding stationery:

Wedding Invitation: 
Size - 140mm x 140mm.

Order of Service: 
Size - 140mm x 190mm. 

Place Card: 
Size - 35mm x 80mm. 

Menu Card: 
Size - 105mm x 155mm. 

Thank You Card: 
Size - 105mm x 155mm. 

WHAT IS INCLUDED IN THE PURCHASE?

You will be able to download the design 'Twittering Love' consisting of invitations, order of service, place cards, menu cards and thank you cards where you can personalize the text for the stationery. 

You will also receive templates for insert pages where you can change the text for your individual use. 

WHAT YOU NEED:

- A printer
- A text processing program such as Word (from Word 2003)
